## Philosophy

> *"Not just better algorithms — a new way of thinking about AI."*

The industry spent 3 years making models bigger. Yann LeCun was right — that was the wrong direction. Real intelligence comes from understanding the world, not memorizing it.

KAIF-Net learns without backpropagation.
LeWM predicts in latent space, not pixels.
SatNam lets humans write AI in the language of mathematics.
GurbaniOptimizer finds grace where SGD gets trapped.

